<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Profile</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <style>
        body        { padding-top:80px; word-wrap:break-word; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

    <div class="page-header text-center">
        <h1><span class="fa fa-anchor"></span> Profile Page</h1>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">Logout</a>
    </div>

    <div class="row">

        <!-- LOCAL INFORMATION -->
        <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
            <div class="well">
		<h3>
			<span class="fa fa-user"></span>
			<strong><%=user.local.email%></strong>
		</h3>
		<p>
			<strong>Windows 7 setup. Only need to setup once.<br></strong>
			Step 1: Click Start menu, in the search box, enter vpn<br>
			Step 2: Select setup a virtual private nework (VPN) connection<br>
			Step 3: Enter 95.215.45.247 in Internet address. Arbitrary in Destination name. Then click Next.<br>
			Step 4: Enter your registered email in Username. enter your registered password in Password. Then click Connect. <br>
			To disconnect and reconnect<br>
			Step 5: Click the network icon on the bottom right of your screen. Select the VPN, disconnect or connect.
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>iPhone/iPad setup. Only need to setup once.<br></strong>
			Step 1: Setting->General->VPN>Add VPN Configuration...<br>
			Step 2: Select PPTP.
			Step 3: Arbitrary name in Description. Enter 95.215.45.247 in Server<br>
			Step 4: enter your registered email in Account. Enter your registered password in Password. Then click Save. <br>
			To disconnect and reconnect<br>
			Step 5: Select the VPN you just setup. Slide the switch on the top to turn on and off of the VPN.
		</p>


